query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ct mc) NoMergeJoin(ct mc t) NoMergeJoin(ct mc t mi) NoMergeJoin(ct mc mi t it) */ select min(t.title) AS american_movie
from company_type AS ct
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' AND mc.note not like '%(TV)%' AND mc.note like '%(USA)%'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1997
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Danish',
'Swedish',
'USA',
'Norway',
'Denmark',
'American',
'Germany',
'German',
'Denish',
'Norwegian')
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id;
